  TERMINAL CORE BRAND PACK 001
  RELEASE DATE: 2026-05-10
  PLATFORM: ANSI TERMINAL / TUI / ASCII ART
  REQUIREMENTS: VT100+ OR MODERN TERMINAL EMULATOR

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  CONTENTS OF THIS PACK:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  * CANONICAL CRAB MASCOT ........ 4 SIZES (TINY/SMALL/MEDIUM/LARGE)
  * BERNARD THE HUMMINGBIRD ...... 3 SIZES, 6 EXPRESSIONS
  * SCUT COMPANION ............... 14 EXPRESSIONS, ANSI-COLORED
  * ANSI LOGO SET ................ SPLASH + WORDMARK + INLINE
  * TUI CHROME ................... BORDERS, BOXES, PILLS, BARS
  * TERMINAL CORE DEMO ........... SELF-CONTAINED PYTHON RENDERER
  * DESIGN SYSTEM SPEC ........... 478-LINE CANONICAL REFERENCE
  * ART TOOLKIT .................. 520-LINE PRODUCTION GUIDE

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  DESIGN PHILOSOPHY:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  NEO-ANSI REVIVAL. INVERSE CORPORATE MEMPHIS. WARM BRUTALISM.
  NOT RETRO-INSPIRED. RETRO-NATIVE. CRAFT, NOT AESTHETIC.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  TECHNICAL NOTES:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - ZERO THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES
  - PYTHON 3.11+ STDLIB-ONLY RENDERER
  - 256-COLOR ANSI WITH 16-COLOR FALLBACK
  - UTF-8 BOX-DRAWING OR ASCII FALLBACK
  - ALL ART VECTOR-READY (CHARACTER-DENSITY BASED)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
